[hardware/3d printed parts/Emla Safe mounting brackets by naaitsab](https://github.com/hugo3132/EmlaLockSafe/tree/master/hardware/3d%20printed%20parts/Emla%20Safe%20mounting%20brackets%20by%20naaitsab)). 

